latestIgtvVideos.caption: #AD To celebrate Disney’s Raya and the Last Dragon streaming on Disney+ for all subscribers (at no extra cost!) latestIgtvVideos.title: My Revlon One Step Volumiser Tutorial
Final Thoughts - Sky SPACETALK watch
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
AD Max has been using his Sky SPACETALK watch since the end of last year and he absolutely loves it.

I asked Max what his favourite feature is and he said it was the step counter and being able to text Daddy funny jokes. For me I’ve found the GPS tracking via the app on my phone really useful especially when Max is on play dates so I know he’s safe.

There’s a link in my stories if you want to find out more about #SkySpaceTalk. It would make the perfect Christmas present 💝

latestIgtvVideos.title: Sky SpaceTalk Watch First Impressions
latestIgtvVideos.caption: AD I’m partnering up with Sky Mobile over the next 6 months to showcase the new SpaceTalk watch for kids. Max has been bugging me for a phone for ages and now the lucky boy has a SpaceTalk watch where he can make two way calls to approved numbers on his contact list, send texts, he can shoot over his location to the All My Tribe app on my phone, check the weather and so much more. What’s even better is there’s no games or internet 👏  #skyspacetalk
